        <item>
            <title>MacBook Air M4 (2025) 搭载 M4 处理器，新「天蓝色」+ 发售日期 + 售价、规格资讯</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/macbook-air-2025-m4/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=macbook-air-2025-m4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/macbook-air-2025-m4/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 14:28:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MacBook Air]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295797</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>继早前 iPad Air, iPad 之后，Apple 在香港时间今晚再发布新产品－－全新 MacBook Air 搭载 M4 晶片。新型号以 M4 晶片为核心，结合轻巧外型与长续航力，方便外出工作长期使用。今次 Apple 为手提电脑推出一款全新颜色「天蓝色」，同样提供 13 吋、15 吋型号，建议零售价由 HK$7,999 起，将于 3 月 12 日发售（现时接受预订）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295799" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/hero_endframe__c67cz-1-694x319.png" alt="" width="694" height="319" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/hero_endframe__c67cz-1-694x319.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/hero_endframe__c67cz-1.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这次 MacBook Air 更新了 M4 晶片，处理速度比上一代更快。晶片内的神经网络引擎也对各类人工智慧功能有一定帮助，从视像通话的人物置中效果，到 AI 协助优化影像，甚至一些大型语言模型的运行，都能发挥更高效率。若本身已是 iPhone 用户，把手机的资料或应用程式状态直接带到电脑上操作更为便利。无论是把 iPhone 上的文字直接复制贴到 MacBook Air，或利用 iCloud 同步照片、文件，两者之间的衔接都十分顺畅。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1295811" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305102733-694x331.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="331" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305102733-694x331.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305102733-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>MacBook Air 除搭载最新 M4 晶片，它最显著的特点之一，是电池可使用至多 18 小时，配合支援快速充电的设计，能在短时间内回复过半电量，对于经常在路上或需要长时间使用电脑的人来说相当实用。此外，MacBook Air 采用无风扇设计，运行时保持安静，从剪辑影片到开启多个应用程式，整体表现都显得流畅。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295804" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_side_skyblue_-1-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_side_skyblue_-1-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_side_skyblue_-1.jpg 1208w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295803" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_portability_1-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_portability_1-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_portability_1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在外型与颜色选择上，新推出的天蓝色为 MacBook Air 带来不同于以往的风格，也保留了银色、星光色及午夜暗色等选项。机身以再生铝金属制造，不仅耐用，还进一步展现了环保意识。无论是 13 吋抑或 15 吋型号，都维持轻薄设计，放进揹包后毫不笨重，带著趴趴走不成问题。对于习惯一次处理多项工作的用家，15 吋萤幕所提供的额外视野更能提升效率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295805" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_right__-694x70.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="70" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_right__-694x70.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_right__.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_left__b-694x80.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="80" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_left__b-694x80.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/connectivity_left__b.jpg 1276w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在显示器方面，MacBook Air 采用 Liquid Retina 技术，能呈现逼真的色彩和细腻的对比度，文字也更清晰。配合高素质的三麦克风与音响设计，不论是视像会议或观赏影片都能提供不错的体验。镜头具备人物置中与桌上视角等功能，开会或线上教学时更方便展示自己的作品或做示范。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295808" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101858-694x413.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="413" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101858-694x413.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101858-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295809" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101908-694x369.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101908-694x369.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250305101908-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295807" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_sizes_endfram-694x524.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="524" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_sizes_endfram-694x524.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_sizes_endfram.jpg 1192w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>扩充能力方面，MacBook Air 配备 MagSafe 充电线，可以轻松吸附在机身上并在需要时迅速脱落，避免被线缠住或扯跌。两个 Thunderbolt 4 连接埠则能连接高速配件或外置显示器，且 Wi‑Fi 6E 带来更快的无线网络速度。在安全性上，Touch ID 功能可快速解锁电脑，或进行购物及付款授权，操作俐落又安全。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295801" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_magsafe_skybl-694x373.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="373" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_magsafe_skybl-694x373.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/design_magsafe_skybl.jpg 960w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Apple 也在这款电脑中加入了 Apple Intelligence 功能，让用家在写文章或整理图片时，能更轻松地进行校对、编修，或利用大型模型产生各式创意图像。值得一提的是，系统非常重视使用者私隐，利用 Mac 上的装置端处理技术和私密云端运算，力求保护个人资料安全。</p><h2>售价与供应</h2><div dir="auto">13 吋$7,999 起</div><div dir="auto">15 吋$9,499 起</div><div dir="auto">立即可预订，3 月 12 日发售</div><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
