        <item>
            <title>日本热乌龙面贩卖机 20 秒出餐，法国网红：「里面有厨师？」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/japan-auto-vendor-20-second-udon/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=japan-auto-vendor-20-second-udon</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/japan-auto-vendor-20-second-udon/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 11:46:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[日本]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[自动贩卖机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294413</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>法国网红 Bebechan 在 IG 分享日本岛根县一台复古乌龙面自动贩卖机，引起网民热议。Bebechan 上传的影片显示，乌龙面自动贩卖机只需 20 秒即可享用热气腾腾的乌龙面，影片吸引不少人讨论其便利与趣味。</p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEziO-HSIyR/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14"><div style="padding: 16px;"><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display: block; height: 50px; margin: 0 auto 12px; width: 50px;"></div><div style="padding-top: 8px;"><div style="color: #3897f0; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 550; line-height: 18px;">在 Instagram 查看这则贴文</div></div><div style="padding: 12.5% 0;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: center;"><div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(7px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; height: 12.5px; transform: rotate(-45deg) translateX(3px) translateY(1px); width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: 8px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"><div style="width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;"><a style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEziO-HSIyR/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bebechan | 日本のフランス人（@bebechan_france）分享的贴文</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//www.instagram.com/embed.js"></script></p><p>这位居日法国网红 Bebechan 在岛根县偶遇复古乌龙面自贩机，投入总值 400 日圆硬币（约港币 21 元）后 20 秒内，热汤面即送到手上。他笑言：「贩卖机里面不会有个师傅吧？」。据悉这类自贩机在日本已有数十年历史，主要设置于乡郊地区，内置加热系统确保食物新鲜。Bebechan 对贩卖机的乌龙面赞不绝口，表示汤底浓郁、肉质鲜甜及面条弹牙。Bebechan 更以熟练筷子技巧示范吃法，获日本网友大赞「比本地人更像日本人」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295416" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noodle1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noodle1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noodle1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Bebechan 在岛根县偶遇复古乌龙面自贩机</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295415" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noodle2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noodle2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noodle2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲投入硬币后可选择肉类，20 秒即可出餐</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295414" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noodle3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noodle3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noodle3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Bebechan 之后更纯熟地使用筷子试食乌龙面，并对这碗面赞不绝口</p><p>这类自贩机虽属旧式设计，却因简单高效而历久不衰。据日本媒体报道，截至 2024 年，全国仍有约 200 台同类机器运作，多数由中小企经营，成为地方经济一环。Bebechan 的影片令外国人惊奇，亦唤起日本人对传统饮食文化的珍惜，不少网友留言推荐其他隐藏美食，如大阪章鱼烧自贩机及北海道热汤罐头。Bebechan 的分享令岛根县这台乌龙面自贩机成为焦点，随着社交媒体传播力增强，这类复古饮食文化或会在年轻一代中重燃兴趣。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://udn.com/news/story/6810/8567240">联合新闻</a>、<a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEziO-HSIyR/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;ig_rid=4d690b27-bc4b-47d6-81f0-78d91af85157">bebechan_france@Instagram</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
